creator: Beyond WS
descriptionHtml:
Fimbre is an Indian originated social recommendation engine. It's a unique platform that enables users to share and discover recommendations with social communities that one is already part of. It allows you to get recommendations that you can trust because they are from people you know rather than anonymous people that you can not relate to. Your Family, Friends, Neighbours, Colleagues and other social connections all have knowledge about so many things that you can use. Fimbre enables to accumulate all that information in a structured way so that everyone in the network can be benefitted. Your social communities might be able to suggest a TV series, place to visit, good doctor for a particular ailment, Mobile app, some restaurant, a Movie, a Hotel and so many other things. Rather then you experimenting yourself or trusting unknown reviews you can get authentic recommendation from your social communities using Fimbre.

Main Features :
* create your soical communities
* share your recommendations under appropriate categories
* discover recommendations from your social communities in a structured way.

descriptionHtml:
Fimbre is India’s first community-based product discovery and recommendation platform.

Buy Smart!!
Looking for the right product but are confused with the diverse choices available in the market? Discover new products based on honest reviews from genuine users and then buy directly from links on Fimbre. Shop amazing products from trusted recommendations.

Join Fimbre!!
* With product reviews posted every minute, Fimbre houses a community of users who interact with fellow members to discover exciting new products.
* Join a community of people just like you. Participate in discussions, answer questions or just ask one.
* Connect & follow like-minded people’s recommendations!
* All recommendations are made by the community, for the community with the help of the community.

Earn!!

KNOW YOU’RE NOT ALONE…

Fimbre is a community-driven app for like-minded people who belong together based-on shared interests and common concerns. Together they discover newer and better tips, remedies, product recommendations, helpful suggestions and many other answers to everyday life challenges.

When people come together in a group and talk about their common issues it brings them closer as a community. It inspires them to do good, by offering help and supporting each others’ journey. Members of the Fimbre community practice this everyday.

JOIN THE FIMBRE COMMUNITY BECAUSE…

—It is designed for people like you seeking simple solutions.
—It is based-on real-life experiences of other members.
—It helps you discover new products when you participate in discussions.

When you connect with community members, you feel supported in your life’s journey and the challenges you face around them. At Fimbre, we’ve created a platform to bring together smaller communities of different interests.

When you participate in discussions, you get recommendations and answers to problems by fellow community members. Cumulative knowledge gained from such discussions leads to harnessing the power of community at large.

When you actively engage, you create connections with other members. You can also follow them if you like their answers and product recommendations. It is these conversations that help build a strong and trusted support system for everyone.

Once you have joined a community of your choice, you can start interacting with fellow community members, and ask them about their experience of having tried a product or any home remedy.

WE CREATED THE FIMBRE COMMUNITY FOR…

Every community at Fimbre is specific to a focused vision, and we closely monitor its content to make it more user-friendly. As a moderated community, it is for the people, of the people, by the people.

Two of our most popular and actively growing communities are Moms & Babies and Beauty & Wellness. For a long time, it is the women who have been leading the growth of these two communities. However, we constantly work on making more meaningful communities.

We’re currently working on introducing new app features like discussions tab, daily tips, awareness posts and product polls which will help better community connections.

Install Fimbre and join the community of your choice to belong, discover and inspire.
Let’s build a community of trusted Fimbreans!

Belong to a powerful community. Discover relevant answers. Inspire others by engaging.

descriptionHtml:
WHAT IS FIMBRE?

Fimbre is an app for communities that brings people together based on similar interests. Here, the community members help each other make choices by sharing queries and recommendations.

As you join a community at Fimbre, you connect with people who help make your buying decisions simpler or who need support while going through similar situations in life. By getting valuable recommendations from these members, you make better choices.

At Fimbre, you will also find discussions about doctors, repairs, beauty brands or amazing shopping experiences. You can contribute to the community by giving suggestions and recommendations of your favorite products, food, books, movies, picnic spots, outdoor activities and more!

WHY JOIN THE COMMUNITIES ON FIMBRE?

— To connect with people having similar interests.
— To find recommendations from people you can trust.
— To ask your query from people whom you can relate to.
— To share experiences and build your followership.
— To feel empowered as the community has your back.

HOW JOINING THE COMMUNITY WILL HELP YOU?
